# Binary assets must never get line-ending conversion — CRLF injection would
# corrupt a font or image. Git usually auto-detects binaries, but on Windows with
# core.autocrlf it can warn/convert, so mark them explicitly.
*.ttf   binary
*.otf   binary
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.pdf   binary
